
# update a merge request

⚠️  do not use 'git commit --amend' to update a branch with an open MR

$[issue-branch] git status // confirm the files that have uncommited changes

$[issue-branch] git add -A // stage all the files with changes

$[issue-branch] git commit -m '{your commit message}' // make a standard commit + one-line message

$[issue-branch] git push

> when you push additinal commits to an MR they will be squashed on merge

